{"tid":521550,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(王者出擊) 何猷君笑住被林志玲畫花面　最緊要女神高興","createTime":"2018-01-06T16:08:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-08T03:03:38.000Z","uid":156068,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cf9aee1a844a7f0d0edeff4180eeb40a92c63464","tid":521550,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T16:08:27.000Z","msg":"有樣有學歷嘅何猷君近期成為內地綜藝目常客，《愛的時差》同《最強大腦之燃燒吧大腦》雖然屬於不同類似的綜藝節目，但何猷君一樣完美地「消化」，有網友更因而視佢為理想型，亦有網友被佢腦力所吸引。<br />\n <br />\n何猷君早前就話過自己係因為超模奚夢瑤關係所以參演《愛的時差》，而其實除咗《愛》之外，由王者榮耀衍生的真人騷《王者出擊》，兩位亦都有份參與。之不過，喺最新一集中，兩個無得拍住一齊上，而何猷君執行任務時遇上林志玲，兼要被對方塗口紅，雖然搞到不男不女，但佢就一啲都無嬲，而且仲好鬼開心，之後當佢聽到林志玲嘅任務係要得到何猷君唇印時，更即時一臉花痴表示：「這是我最開心的時刻。」幫忙志玲姐姐完成任務之後，何猷君即時被out，但佢就笑晒同跳住咁話:「我很開心。」賺錢賺人氣兼可以一親女神，即時明晒點解何猷君要參加咁多綜藝。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/07/000813_dd01f74ac0d52829c783f77502aef900.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F07%2F000813_dd01f74ac0d52829c783f77502aef900.jpg&h=f554b3f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/07/000817_197811f065e4e5ef2683dd0d87c3a769.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F07%2F000817_197811f065e4e5ef2683dd0d87c3a769.jpg&h=bdc76b9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/07/000822_6708ad23c610cd95ece3aad6b340f41a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F07%2F000822_6708ad23c610cd95ece3aad6b340f41a.jpg&h=e65bd6f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"992ad2ca048b3cb606a61f1deb793f55e7d95261","tid":521550,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T16:32:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ad4b3c2eff49860a7de81b7b9cc76599d69b96","tid":521550,"uid":29702